{"tid":423012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日AV新創舉　女優背氧氣筒在海裡「啪啪啪」","createTime":"2017-10-03T14:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T10:00:23.000Z","uid":41351,"like":427,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"1abd30154979ea85f0e8d2a1dbbdb0199392dbff","tid":423012,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:33:40.000Z","msg":"日本AV又有新突破！這次真的拚命了！<br />\n<br />\n日本成人影視產業發達，常常有許多創新題材令人耳目一新，「AV達人」一劍浣春秋日前在部落格「playno1」介紹一部由知名AV女優水野朝陽主演的新片，企劃令人昨舌！<br />\n<br />\n從新片預覽圖中可以看到片商將整個場景搬到了海邊，但可不是在海邊沙灘「啪啪啪」這麼單純，女優、男優以及拍攝工作人員全都下海，男女優揹著氧氣筒、戴上呼吸面罩在大海裡激戰，而且一劍浣春秋透露「雖然沒辦法口愛，但其他該做的事情都有做！」，令人不禁佩服男女優的戰鬥力以及片商的大膽創新。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171003/1215968/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20171003%2F1215968%2F&d=AkPnqzfnUBV65atxb%2FxpEviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9c2cc40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20171003/1215968/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/223234_d37376e0e1ca260f24c0688da1d8007e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F223234_d37376e0e1ca260f24c0688da1d8007e.jpg&h=e0876ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/223234_cf9e3528ef1b59cdb719f673c4b42adf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F223234_cf9e3528ef1b59cdb719f673c4b42adf.jpg&h=26e55d96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚污糟，會不會比魚食左條蟲蟲"},{"pid":"cbe6ee610d0bbe3790ad5d13853be4c55b3ae3f4","tid":423012,"uid":13149,"like":426,"dislike":3,"score":423,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時會拍到上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma